          <title>Novice climber survives 1,500-foot drop on California's Mount Shasta after helicopter rescue delayed by clouds</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Climbing rangers hiked up Mount Shasta on foot after cloud cover blocked a direct helicopter rescue of a woman who slid 1,500 feet down Avalanche Gulch.]]></description>
