          <title>16 children rescued from Ohio home were 'almost feral,' authorities say</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Authorities say 16 children from the same family who were rescued from a run-down home in rural Ohio were living in horrific conditions and were confined to just one room over much of the past four years.]]></description>
